body_html: @ali01 @petewarden So, adding the cwise_op_less_equal.cc fixed the first issue, but then Missing op... "RandomUniform" came up and this was due to the use of dropout ops. Removing these fixed the issue. This time, I skipped the inference optimization step on the frozen graph to be safe and it built and works.

body: @ali01 @petewarden  So, adding the `cwise_op_less_equal.cc` fixed the first issue, but then `Missing op... "RandomUniform"` came up and this was due to the use of `dropout` ops. Removing these fixed the issue. This time, I skipped the inference optimization step on the frozen graph to be safe and it built and works.
